title: WarioWare-ing with Ron Funches
description: Honorary Besties Ron Funches joins us once again to discuss the latest opus from Mario's pungent counterpart, WarioWare: Get It Together. Other games discussed include: Splitgate, Final Fantasy V, The Forgotten City, Deathloop (briefly!) and a whole mess of other WarioWare games!
author: thebestiesbizemail@gmail.com (Ron Funches, Chris Plante, Russ Frushtick, Griffin McElroy)
